{"tid":2095201,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[少甜包膠] 網友分享英國叫鴨心得","createTime":"2020-07-05T09:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T04:51:04.000Z","uid":44725,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59dd29a9a1134f9d0137e3b280f2bae22f27fb5a","tid":2095201,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"英國有唔少叫鴨網站，叫鴨同叫雞一樣普遍流行，同香港唔同既係，大部係鴨仔都係真相無加工，明碼實價，寫到明有Ｄ咩做得咩唔會做，有分 1 小時，2 小時，甚至過夜收費。唔少鴨仔都係兼職，每個人都有唔同理由下海，部份搵快錢，部份搵學費，只有少部份當係一份正職，但係大部份都好敬業，唔似大陸果Ｄ快快趣完事就趕你走。<br />\n<br />\n鴨仔收費因人而異，上年紀的會平好多，因為冇市場。以年輕既來講，通常一小時收 100-200 鎊，過夜就 500-1000 鎊不等，有Ｄ仲會可以一齊去旅行。<br />\n<br />\n佢地鴨仔英文叫 Escort 唔係 Prostitute，話自己係提供陪伴服務，佢地服務對象唔一定係男性，過程中係可以冇性交易，呢個視客人需求。<br />\n<br />\n網友自己係英國搵過幾隻鴨仔，過夜就有一次。呢仔鴨仔 19 歲，正職係拍 Gay 片，住係英國東南部一小鎮。去英國前同佢 Whatsapp 傾好左，約左佢係倫敦等，佢就坐左４個鐘火車去倫敦。既然係 Gay 片主角，又過夜，收費當然唔平。約左佢係帕丁頓車站等，佢黎到已經擁抱，仲話急不及待返酒店開波，取消左本來一齊去白金漢宮既行程。返到酒店大戰左一個鐘後，佢就話肚餓一齊食晚餐，果時然已經係下午６點。"},{"pid":"54bfe61e408bf23f3060a2eff71a2bd1a4d760a5","tid":2095201,"uid":44725,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"晚餐後當然返酒店繼續大戰，去到 11 點左右就訓教。過程中除左做愛之外，都有一齊睇電視，傾偈等，佢仲話我係佢最年輕的客人之一，仲話會搵一個男人結婚，我會係佢考慮對象之一。訓醒後就一齊落去食早餐，然後當然繼續再上床，到早上 9 點半左右就結束，各散東西，佢就要飛去其它國家繼續拍片。佢話佢拍一套片可以賺 500 鎊。<br />\n<br />\n總括來講，佢係一隻好好既鴨仔，已經約好左下次見面地點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/05/8w9Zdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2F8w9Zdy.jpg&h=5591caa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/05/gK42s5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2FgK42s5.jpg&h=d57fa2f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/05/rMNRf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2FrMNRf0.jpg&h=f0b7158d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/05/T23I6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F05%2FT23I6G.jpg&h=8bcd2334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"435924f2368dff2d59363f64eb3765b2cfab88c3","tid":2095201,"uid":240976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"我要仔仔既圖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a4468cb68966bf5d9d0078da094a9193557364","tid":2095201,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855432f564e87fbde52cf7e7e0685c7fbcd19b5a","tid":2095201,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"諗起呢篇<br />\n<br />\n網友分享東京叫鴨心得 (包膠)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/418419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/418419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5cd9b92579de911ed44f53ca34c08dbd1b8597d0","tid":2095201,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18ac2ec9e8e9b6a2ce6abe6c9df7684bb4a55bf","tid":2095201,"uid":35301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"855432f564e87fbde52cf7e7e0685c7fbcd19b5a","tid":2095201,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"諗起呢篇<br />\n<br />\n網友分享東京叫鴨心得 (包膠)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/418419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/418419</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"都係樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ce5c28f1b3329a4a044186f6045517b80a0ef5","tid":209520